    end

    %% External flows
    Client -->|"gRPC/8033<br/>Optional TLS<br/>Optional mTLS"| ModelMesh
    Client -->|"HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS (serving cert)<br/>OAuth Bearer token"| OAuthProxy

    %% Internal pod flows
    OAuthProxy -->|"HTTP/8008<br/>plaintext (pod-local)<br/>SAR check passed"| RESTProxy
    RESTProxy -->|"gRPC/8033<br/>Optional TLS (pod-local)"| ModelMesh
    ModelMesh -->|"gRPC<br/>plaintext (pod-local)"| ModelServer
    ModelMesh -->|"gRPC/8086<br/>plaintext (pod-local)"| Puller

    %% Inter-pod
    ModelMesh -->|"gRPC/8080<br/>LiteLinks<br/>plaintext<br/>NetworkPolicy restricted"| ModelMeshB

    %% Controller flows
    Controller -->|"gRPC/8033<br/>VModel API"| ModelMesh
    Controller -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>SA token"| K8sAPI
    Controller -->|"gRPC/2379<br/>Event stream<br/>Basic auth"| etcd

    %% Runtime to external
    ModelMesh -->|"gRPC/2379<br/>plaintext/TLS<br/>Basic auth"| etcd
    Puller -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>S3 credentials"| S3
    OAuthProxy -->|"HTTPS<br/>TLS<br/>Token validation"| OpenShiftOAuth

    %% Monitoring
    Prometheus -.->|"scrape 2112/TCP"| ModelMesh
    Prometheus -.->|"scrape 8080/TCP"| Controller

    %% Webhook
    K8sAPI -->|"HTTPS/9443<br/>TLS<br/>API server cert"| Controller

